(8, 'library', 'লাইব্রেরি', 'খোন্দকার দেলোয়ার হোসেন কলেজের লাইব্রেরিতে ২০০৩ সাল হতে কলেজে বোর্ড কর্তৃক অনুমদন কৃত পাঠ্য বিষয় সমুহের বই কলেজ লা্ইব্রেরিতে সংরক্ষিত আছে। বিভিন্ন উপন্যাস গল্পের বই লাইব্রেরিতে সংরক্ষিত আছে।সংরক্ষিত আছে বাংলা ও ইংরেজী ডিকসুনারী।', ''),
(9, 'job', 'চাকুরী তথ্য', '<h3>Post Name:  Assistant Teacher</h3>\r\n \r\nNo. of  Vacancies\r\n02\r\nJob Description / Responsibility\r\nDevelop responsive websites using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.\r\nDevelop websites using various CMS and eCommerce platforms.\r\nImplement web application features using PHP.\r\nIntegrate websites to social networking sites like Facebook, Twitter, etc.\r\nDeploy websites to WAMP or LAMP hosting.\r\nJob Nature\r\nFull-time\r\nEducational Requirements\r\nB.Sc or M.Sc in Computer Science/ Engineering or equivalent.\r\nFresh graduates are encouraged to apply.\r\nExperience Requirements\r\nAt least 1 year(s)\r\nAdditional Job Requirements\r\nMust have strong knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.\r\nMust have strong knowledge Bootstrap.\r\nMust be familiar with any CMS, like WordPress, Joomla, SilverStripe, etc.\r\nFamiliarity with jQuery and AJAX is preferred.\r\nMust have strong communication skills in English, both written and spoken.\r\nMust be able to learn new technologies, tools, and techniques quickly and with minimal supervision.\r\nMust be proactive and able to execute tasks efficiently.\r\nApply Instruction\r\n\r\nIf you meet the above requirements, please send us your updated resume and portfolio to the following email address:\r\ncareer@schoolDomain.edu.bd\r\nOnly short listed candidates will be called for interview.', '');

